&lt;b&gt;3. Locking onto Asia from anywhere in the World &lt;/b&gt;
&gt;By acquiring networks that have good &lt;u&gt;lines across different areas across the World&lt;/u&gt;, it allows for better fine-tuning and improving of routes.

